description: Nothing satisfies your taste buds like a Taste of Texas BBQ! Colorado will never be the same after digging into this real downhome cuisine. Ribs, wings, pulled pork, Creole-style crawfish and more are being expertly seasoned and cooked to perfection at this fantastic trailer! If you're looking for the finest food North of the Lone Star State, it's got to be Taste of Texas BBQ!
name: Taste of Texas BBQ
